CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: The Operating Entity, established in September 2016, is engaged in the research, development, manufacturing, and sales of injection molding machine-dedicated manipulator arms. It is also a provider of installation services and warranty services for manipulator arms, and accessories and raw materials for manipulator arms.
